name: POSTLIVING V KRIS DOUGLAS COASTERS
description:
set of  6 coasters designed by Kristian Douglas and only available 
here at PostLiving.
all coasters are made of 3mm laser cut foamex ,measure 90mm x 90mm and finished by hand.they are printed on both sides.the top of each coaster has the artitsts work and the base of the coaster is finished with a PostLiving design.
they are mailed out by registered post and we aim to have the coasters to you within one week.
they are £10 per pack inc P&P
